恨；去甲方单位干活儿，对方提出不合理的要求导致他加班他觉得愤怒，但对方提出帮他打出租车时，他又很不好意思地客客气气，就很容易被拿捏… 这是什么心理？老实人这种心理又是怎样形成的？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-baff28f3998f134ffd1250d64b349f0c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652586232"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIxuWHoaTXhOtBEAMaCTEwNzI5NjY5OSDW1d2wBjAAOL8BQClyCTY1MjU4NjIzMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1713227815.955238", "card_id": "Q_494690677", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 185}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《孤儿怨》、《坏种》、《我的小公主》这类片子真的应该让小孩子演吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "故事情节那么成人，演员就不会有心理阴影吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-65e3488d9fc6bb079eb2b7a17f5aa8b0_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/494690677"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IxuWHoaTXhOtBEAMaCDcyMjEyMTE1IIi234sGMAA4pwZAKnIJNDk0NjkwNjc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1713227815.956113", "card_id": "Q_653016420", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 63}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么都说护肤得保持好心情，个人情绪真的会影响到皮肤健康吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "发现大多数的情绪压力都源自生活、工作，负面情绪堆积多了对皮肤也会造成损害。听到有朋友使用藏红花精油修复受损皮肤，想知道大家是如何进行健康护肤的？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653016420"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IxuWHoaTXhOtBEAMaCTEwNzM5MjM3NSDYxPOwBjAAOGhAK3IJNjUzMDE2NDIweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", 